==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Adolescence
<hw>Ad`o*les"cence</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Fr., fr. L.
<ets>adolescentia</ets>.]</ety> <def>The state of growing up from
childhood to manhood or womanhood; youth, or the period of life between
puberty and maturity, generally considered to be, in the male sex, from
fourteen to twenty-one. Sometimes used with reference to the lower
animals.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Adolescency</ent>⟦br⟧
